    <p>When I'm not writing code, I dedicate my time to my other great passion: rock climbing.<br> I started climbing in September 2007: love at first sight!</p>

    <p>The bad thing is that I started at the age of 32 (sigh!), the good thing is that climbing changed my life.
      This may seem like an overstatement, but it's real! Climbing changed my habits, my friendships and the way I
      spend my time during the week.</p>

    <p>Climbing is really important to me and I'm putting a lot of effort in it, trying to push the limits to see
